    Single Incision Needle Knife Biopsy for the Diagnosis of Gastrointestinal Subepithelial Tumors: A Systematic Review and Meta-Analysis.
SINK biopsy is a safe diagnostic procedure with a high technical and diagnostic success in patients with gastrointestinal SET. Further randomized controlled trials and direct comparison studies are needed to validate these findings.
